{"tid":880171,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"八年前香討一篇\"買樓10大誤解\"理論, 今\b日係連登正式宣佈破滅","createTime":"2018-10-28T14:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T07:06:55.000Z","uid":214872,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c6044131c5d76160b73219e9effdb2cc6ed48d26","tid":880171,"uid":214872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"原文連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=13408120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D13408120&d=S3hZbgsybcF0tVxnO%2BU3IHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ae5d8dd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=13408120</a><br />\n<br />\n7個月前有人post返上連登, 個個仲當呢篇文既理論係神咁拜<br />\n覺得8年前已經有人講中晒, 過千正評<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586245/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586245/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n11日前有人quote返同一段, 已經個個屌樓主講既野on9<br />\n俾到好多好有理據既反駁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/865244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/865244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n可想而知 今次跌市令好多連登仔睇清晒樓市真面目<br />\n唔好再相信呢八年黎所講既咩&quot;大跌市時買平樓，你要有好多現金&quot;, &quot;以20~30年長線睇，樓價一定升&quot;, &quot;供樓係會越來越輕鬆&quot;<br />\n根本就係假<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多人笑連登仔買唔起樓先睇淡<br />\n但可以一兩個月既跌市中睇清其他業主相信左八年既既理論<br />\n連登仔先係最聰明個班(好友唔好再影衰連登, 唔該)"},{"pid":"c726bcd70cdbd902f379dcb9c34ad05a1670059e","tid":880171,"uid":171192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"專家食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2ed327aeb57ecea4a35ae031a04b940ca5be44","tid":880171,"uid":214872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c726bcd70cdbd902f379dcb9c34ad05a1670059e","tid":880171,"uid":171192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"專家食屎啦<img src=\"/ass